            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                ἀγ<supplied reason="lost">αθὴ</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">τύχη</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Γ(αίῳ) Πουβλικίῳ Προκου<lb break="no" n="3"/>ληιάνῳ Ῥαβεννήτῃ <lb n="4"/>πριμιπειλαρίῳ ἐπιτρόπῳ <lb n="5"/>Παιονίας καὶ Ἀχαιίας ἡ <lb n="6"/>ἱερὰ πόλις Δελφῶν <lb n="7"/>ἀνέστησεν <lb n="8"/>ψ(ηφίσματι) β(ουλῆς)</ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Publicio <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cam</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Raven</supplied>na Proculeiano <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ulla </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ἀγ<supplied reason="lost">αθὴ</supplied> <supplied reason="lost">τύχη</supplied> Νουμέρι
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Es fehlen sowohl das Bruchstück [---]ulla am Ende als auch der Text auf Seite B.</p>
            </div>
